{"title":"win7下用xampp部署php项目","date":"2018-05-03T00:15:00.000Z","link":"post/58","tags":["config","db'","master'","p","php","xampp","数据库","文件","目录"],"categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:31:53.822Z","content":"<h2 id=\"1、下载xampp安装\">1、下载xampp安装<a href=\"post/58#1、下载xampp安装\"></a></h2><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/2397354493.png\" alt=\"xampp\" class=\"article-img\"><br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"2、设置apache的conf文件\">2、设置apache的conf文件<a href=\"post/58#2、设置apache的conf文件\"></a></h2><p><code>D:\\xampp\\apache\\conf</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"修改：\">修改：<a href=\"post/58#修改：\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">DocumentRoot &quot;D:/weikang/weikang_system/src&quot; //你项目地址目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;Directory &quot;D:/weikang/weikang_system/src&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   .....</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/Directory&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"添加：\">添加：<a href=\"post/58#添加：\"></a></h3><p>在<code>&lt;IfModule mime_module&gt;</code>最后中添加<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">AddHandler application/x-httpd-php .php</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AddType   application/x-httpd-php  .php  .html  .htm</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LoadModule php7_module D:/xampp/php/php7apache2_4.dll //确定你的php版本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;IfModule mime_module&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\">   ......</span><br><span class=\"line\">   </span><br><span class=\"line\">    AddHandler application/x-httpd-php .php</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AddType   application/x-httpd-php  .php  .html  .htm</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LoadModule php7_module D:/xampp/php/php7apache2_4.dll</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/IfModule&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>参考文章：<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/convincee/p/6636760.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.cnblogs.com/convincee/p/6636760.html</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"3、修改项目目录中conf文件（config-php）修改数据库地址\">3、修改项目目录中conf文件（config.php）修改数据库地址<a href=\"post/58#3、修改项目目录中conf文件（config-php）修改数据库地址\"></a></h3><p><code>D:\\weikang\\weikang_system\\src\\data\\config.php</code><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;host&apos;] = &apos;数据库ip&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;username&apos;] = &apos;用户&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;password&apos;] = &apos;密码&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;port&apos;] = &apos;3306&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;database&apos;] = &apos;weikang&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;charset&apos;] = &apos;utf8&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;pconnect&apos;] = 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$config[&apos;db&apos;][&apos;master&apos;][&apos;tablepre&apos;] = &apos;ims_&apos;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"apache实现二级域名访问不同项目目录","link":"post/62"},"next":{"title":"Tomcat启动成功没有报错，但网页打不开","link":"post/55"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/58/","toc":[{"title":"1、下载xampp安装","id":"1、下载xampp安装","index":"1"},{"title":"2、设置apache的conf文件","id":"2、设置apache的conf文件","index":"2","children":[{"title":"修改：","id":"修改：","index":"2.1"},{"title":"添加：","id":"添加：","index":"2.2"},{"title":"3、修改项目目录中conf文件（config.php）修改数据库地址","id":"3、修改项目目录中conf文件（config-php）修改数据库地址","index":"2.3"}]}]}